<div class="title">A Mild Experience</div>
<div class="substance">AMT</div>
<div class="author">by <a href="/experiences/exp.cgi?A=Search&AuthorSearch=Brendan&Exact=1">Brendan</a></div>


<div class="ts-citation">Citation:&nbsp;&nbsp; Brendan. "A Mild Experience: An Experience with AMT (exp17315)". <u>Erowid.org</u>. Sep 9, 2002. erowid.org/exp/17315</div>

